Implementation Plan: Reusable QR + WhatsApp Ordering System

Goal
Build the simplest reusable mobile-first QR + WhatsApp ordering web app for small Indian businesses using React + Vite frontend, Google Apps Script backend, Google Sheets database, and official WhatsApp API provider.

Mandatory Architecture
React + Vite frontend
→ Google Apps Script Web App API
→ Google Sheets database
→ Official WhatsApp Business API provider
→ Optional SMS backup later

Tech Stack
Frontend:
- React
- Vite
- JavaScript
- Simple CSS first; Tailwind only if already installed
- Mobile-first responsive layout

Backend:
- Google Apps Script Web App
- doPost endpoint for order submission
- Optional doGet endpoint for health check or menu fetch if needed

Database:
- Google Sheets

Hosting:
- Vercel preferred for simplest deployment
- Firebase Hosting or Netlify acceptable

WhatsApp:
- WATI, Interakt, Twilio, Gupshup, AiSensy, or 360dialog
- Abstract provider integration so it can be replaced later

